'''加迪迈节'''（{{lang-ne|गढ़िमाई पर्व}}，{{lang-en|Gadhimai festival}}），是在[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]{{link-en|巴拉 (尼泊尔)|Bara District|巴拉县}}{{link-en|巴里亚尔普尔 (巴拉县)|Bariyarpur, Bara|巴里亚尔普尔}}[[加迪迈庙|加迪迈庙]]举办的一个[[印度教|印度教]]节日，每5年举办一次。

==简介==
在这个节日中，加迪迈庙及所在地区会举行大规模的[[祭祀|祭祀]]仪式，献祭大量动物以求加迪迈女神保佑人们各自实现自己的愿望。<ref name="myref3">{{Cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Indians-throng-Nepals-Gadhimai-fair-for-animal-sacrifice/articleshow/5264701.cms?referral=PM|title=Indians throng Nepal's Gadhimai fair for animal sacrifice|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=Times of India|archive-date=2014-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141023114331/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Indians-throng-Nepals-Gadhimai-fair-for-animal-sacrifice/articleshow/5264701.cms?referral=PM|dead-url=no}}</ref>大约200万人参加该节日，[[梅德西人|梅德西人]]以及超过80%的信徒都是从[[印度|印度]][[比哈尔邦|比哈尔邦]]和[[北方邦|北方邦]]来的。在尼泊尔参加节日，可以不受印度各邦对动物献祭的禁令的限制。<ref name="th">{{cite news|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/international/article53883.ece|title=Gadhimai festival begins despite protests in Nepal|date=24 November 2009|work=The Hindu|accessdate=24 November 2009|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701064944/http://www.thehindu.com/news/international/article53883.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="toi">{{cite news|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-11-24/south-asia/28087161_1_porous-indo-nepal-border-maoist-mp-nepal-government|title=Indians throng Nepal's Gadhimai fair for animal sacrifice|last=Sarkar|first=Sudeshna|date=24 November 2009|work=The Times of India|accessdate=24 November 2009|archive-date=2013-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813193104/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2009-11-24/south-asia/28087161_1_porous-indo-nepal-border-maoist-mp-nepal-government|dead-url=no}}</ref>参加者们相信，向加迪迈女神献祭动物可以消灾得福。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/11/20/gadhimai-festival-nepal-m_n_364790.html|title=Gadhimai Festival: Nepal Mass Animal Sacrifice Festival To Go Ahead Despite Protests|date=20 November 2009|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=25 November 2009|last=Gurubacharya|first=Binaj|archive-date=2015-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150702062023/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2009/11/20/gadhimai-festival-nepal-m_n_364790.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="myref2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30250517|title=In pictures: Hindu animal sacrifice festival in Nepal|accessdate=28 November 2014|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2015-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328034531/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30250517|dead-url=no}}</ref>

仪式在黎明开始，首先进行“潘恰巴利”（pancha bali）即献祭五只动物，包括一只老鼠，一头山羊，一只公鸡，一头猪，一只鸽子。<ref name="myref4">{{Cite web|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report-nepal-s-gadhimai-festival-hindu-devotees-sacrifice-thousands-of-animals-in-ritual-2039206|title=Nepal's Gadhimai festival: Hindu devotees sacrifice thousands of animals in ritual|accessdate=28 November 2014|publisher=dna india|archive-date=2015-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424161327/http://www.dnaindia.com/world/report-nepal-s-gadhimai-festival-hindu-devotees-sacrifice-thousands-of-animals-in-ritual-2039206|dead-url=no}}</ref>在整个节日期间，家养雄性亚洲[[水牛|水牛]]（当地人称“PaaDa”）是最热门的献祭动物，其他献祭动物还有公山羊（Khassi/Boka），鸡（Murga/Kukhura），鸽子（Parewa），鸭（Haans），[[大鼠|大鼠]]（Moos）等，这些动物被全部杀死。<ref name="myref1">{{Cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8375591.stm|title=Devotees flock to Nepal animal sacrifice festival|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=BBC News|archive-date=2009-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126040719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8375591.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>据估计，2009年加迪迈节期间，有30万到50万只动物被杀死<ref name="myref6">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/nov/24/hindu-sacrifice-gadhimai-festival-nepal|title=Hindu sacrifice of 250,000 animals begins|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=The Guardian|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107054804/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/nov/24/hindu-sacrifice-gadhimai-festival-nepal|dead-url=no}}</ref>，50万人来该庙参观<ref name=cnn20091124>{{Cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/11/24/nepal.animal.sacrifice/index.html|title=Ritual animal slaughter begins in Nepal|accessdate=November 24, 2009|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107171059/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/11/24/nepal.animal.sacrifice/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。加迪迈节被认为是世界上最大规模的动物献祭。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-hans | publisher = 网易探索 | title = 尼泊尔宰牲节残忍杀死20万头牲畜 | url = http://discover.news.163.com/09/1126/11/5P1TPLA2000125LI.html | date = 2009-11-26 | accessdate = 2011-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110718024521/http://discover.news.163.com/09/1126/11/5P1TPLA2000125LI.html | archive-date = 2011-07-18 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="myref1"/>

2009年节日前1个月，马德西人政治家们意识到将会遇到献祭用山羊的“严重短缺”，以及节日期间用于食用的山羊肉的“严重短缺”。他们用广播劝说农民们出售他们的牲畜，以缓解短缺局面。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8256723.stm|title=Nepal hit by severe goat shortage|date=15 September 2009|work=BBC|accessdate=25 November 2009|archive-date=2015-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150420144211/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8256723.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

若干动物权利活动人士在每次举办加迪迈节之前及之中反对该节日。2009年加迪迈节引起了[[玛妮卡·甘地|玛妮卡·甘地]]、[[碧姬·芭铎|碧姬·芭铎]]等知名人士的关注，他们齐齐反对这种大规模杀戮动物的行为。<ref name="myref3">{{Cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/Indians-throng-Nepals-Gadhimai-fair-for-animal-sacrifice/articleshow/5264701.cms?referral=PM|title=Indians throng Nepal's Gadhimai fair for animal sacrifice|accessdate=24 November 2009|publisher=Times of India}}</ref>尼泊尔政府官员表示，他们不能阻止许多世纪延续下来的这种传统，尽管尼泊尔和印度的动物权利活动人士对此表示反对。动物权利活动人士说，他们不指望一夜之间就结束这种行为。<ref name=cnn20091124/><ref name="myref2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-30250517|title=In pictures: Hindu animal sacrifice festival in Nepal|accessdate=28 November 2014 |publisher=BBC News}}</ref>

